# APi Sign in

curl --location 'http://localhost:3080/sign-in' \
--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "password": "123456",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}'

# API Login

--header 'Content-Type: application/json' \
--data-raw '{
    "password": "123456",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}'
